{
  "texts": [
    "These representations were then further processed via three linear layers with ReLU nonlinearities.",
    "We trained the GNN with four GPUs, 90 CPUs, a batch size of 50 and for 50 epochs.",
    "We evaluated the best models on the MISATO affinity benchmark using Spearman correlation on each set.",
    "We used PyTorch v.1.14 to train the models.",
    "To code the data loaders and the GNN, we used PyTorch Geometric 2.3.0."
  ]
}